description:
In a world where endless traffic jams and often very slow drivers sometimes, you are want to relax, spit on it all, go out of town or to start squeezing everything out of your car ? So why don't do it ? Do you want to feel adrenaline and to overcome traffic at a huge speed? Welcome to Redline: Unlimited!

Here you are expected:

• More than 15 perfectly detailed machines! 
• Huge speed, sometimes exceeding 300 km/h! 
• 4 well-developedd endless tracks; 
• Excellent graphics; 
• User-friendly interface; 
• Convenient control; 
• Exciting modes of play; 
• Adrenaline and more!

Redline: Unlimited - Unlimited Speed!
